summaries.short: A detective investigates the murder of an 11-year-old boy, but is baffled by the strong alibi of his main suspect.
summaries.full: Series premiere. When the body of an 11-year-old boy is found in the Georgia woods, detective Ralph Anderson launches an investigation into the gruesome murder. With eyewitnesses and physical evidence pointing to local teacher and baseball coach Terry Maitland, Ralph makes a very public arrest but is perplexed by Terry's seeming indifference to hiding his crime.
